Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.18,0:00:22.74,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的轉輪不停地旋轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.89,0:00:31.29,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我永遠注視著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.03,0:00:40.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何  我如此  三生有幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.03,0:00:46.97,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每見到水平線  便有莫名哀傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.13,0:00:56.56,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠遠地回首 過去的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.72,0:00:59.98,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限感傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.89,0:01:06.82,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的轉輪不停地旋轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.98,0:01:13.20,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠深入思考的只有  Mystery
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.49,0:01:19.75,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  命中的良人就在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.91,0:01:26.47,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我  一直守候你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.62,0:01:35.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我  一直守候你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.58,0:22:34.74,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想嘗試如履薄冰般危險的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.89,0:22:41.41,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好希望心中描繪的夢想能夠成型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.56,0:22:45.33,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forever My Destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.82,0:22:52.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空船如果降臨在自己面前 我一定會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.03,0:22:59.72,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拋下朋友  離開地球展開旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.00,0:23:08.64,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說平靜的每一天就是幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.80,0:23:18.90,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我其實想逃  我害怕沒有你的每一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.06,0:23:27.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像如履薄冰般  偷偷地  戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.65,0:23:34.13,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心飛向你的速度比光速更快更遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.28,0:23:38.09,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forever My Destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.20,0:00:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人與人的邂逅充滿了神奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.80,0:00:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種刑案更是謎題重重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.50,0:00:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠遇到你真的是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.50,0:00:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天登場的是美人姐妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.20,0:00:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室裏發生了案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.20,0:00:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.60,0:00:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.60,0:00:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.60,0:00:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.80,0:01:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室密室事件(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.70,0:02:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.10,0:02:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼晚才回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.50,0:02:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在便利商店裏耽擱了一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.40,0:02:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你要我買的東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.00,0:02:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看我全部買到了喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.20,0:02:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室清潔劑、膠帶還有啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.30,0:02:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我連浴室清潔劑都給忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.30,0:02:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家附近的便利店最近正好在裝修呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.00,0:02:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們之前錄的那些偶像劇的錄影帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.70,0:02:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都要帶走嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.40,0:02:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.60,0:02:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老姐我這次可是為了你才搬離這裏的不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.80,0:02:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東西可真不少啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.90,0:02:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.30,0:02:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.50,0:02:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就幫我把膠帶剪成適當的長度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貼在桌子的邊緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.30,0:02:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我待會兒封箱的時候就方便了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.60,0:02:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.30,0:02:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然跑到這裏來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.60,0:03:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要你幫我買東西和打包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.30,0:03:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客氣什麼嘛 跟我說這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.10,0:03:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來還要謝謝你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.30,0:03:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天那場演唱會賢二盼了好久了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.30,0:03:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我差點忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們打包之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要為我這個沉浸在幸福之中的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.20,0:03:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好幹一杯才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…不用了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.90,0:03:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從你們兩個決定要結婚之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.50,0:03:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直很忙 還沒祝福你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.80,0:03:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以姐姐正好趁現在這個機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.30,0:03:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就別推辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.40,0:04:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗大方的洋子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.10,0:04:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的美麗真是一種罪過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.20,0:04:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到沒 這是我特地為你準備的玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.70,0:04:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是哪一朵都是因為等著看你而被染得通紅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.20,0:04:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.60,0:04:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒覺得大叔這幅傻樣才叫罪過呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.70,0:04:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這小鬼對於大人的這種浪漫說法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.70,0:04:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.50,0:04:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也叫浪漫的說法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.00,0:04:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔今天的心情好像特別好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.00,0:04:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天有沖野洋子的演唱會嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.40,0:04:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.60,0:04:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們該過去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.20,0:04:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱會現場那裏可是擠滿了人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.70,0:04:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在瞎擔什麼心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.10,0:05:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要把洋子小姐送的簽了名的門票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接拿給工作人員看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.60,0:05:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就可以直接進去了 不用排…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.40,0:05:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…有個洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.90,0:05:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不是把門票弄丟了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.60,0:05:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.30,0:05:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.40,0:05:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的洋子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.90,0:05:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會在廁所啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔到了這裏以後不是直衝廁所了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…一定是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.60,0:05:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廁所…廁所…廁所…一定在廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 找到了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.50,0:06:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 什麼都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.20,0:06:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.50,0:06:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要跟他們解釋一下說不定還可以進去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.60,0:06:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 我手捧鮮花怎麼可以說出這種丟人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.80,0:06:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.60,0:06:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你下禮拜好像就要期中考試了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.80,0:06:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.00,0:06:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就把你的門票給我 然後你就回家復習功課吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.80,0:06:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.40,0:06:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.00,0:06:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要說門票弄丟了的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.90,0:06:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.60,0:06:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果跟他們說是柯南把門票弄丟的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太過分了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.70,0:06:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你不能來是什麼意思啊 賢二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.30,0:06:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.60,0:06:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你看完了現場演唱會感冒就會好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.30,0:06:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.20,0:06:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了拿到這次沖野洋子演唱會的門票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.60,0:06:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我費了多大的功夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.00,0:06:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之你給我馬上過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.60,0:06:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和我妹妹都已經準備好 坐你的車子一起去演唱會現場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.30,0:07:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 賢二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.20,0:07:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.30,0:07:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個差勁的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.90,0:07:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.90,0:07:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的門票你是不是多了一張啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是指沖野洋子演唱會的門票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.20,0:07:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話能不能麻煩您把多出來的那張票便宜點讓給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.10,0:07:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.20,0:07:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要解釋一下就能進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.60,0:07:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用再買一張了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.10,0:07:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.20,0:07:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人的尊嚴是不能用錢來衡量的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.60,0:07:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死要面子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.20,0:07:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.20,0:07:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然也沒有掉在大叔的車子裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.90,0:07:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張門票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.80,0:07:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.80,0:07:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.50,0:07:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣都請您把那張票讓給我好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.70,0:07:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看錢就不用了 送給你好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.40,0:07:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送給我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.60,0:08:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送給我…真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.60,0:08:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不過有件事可能要麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.30,0:08:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道能不能答應我一件事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 您儘管說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.10,0:08:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔他這是怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.50,0:08:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸本來想用錢買回他男人的尊嚴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.60,0:08:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對方好像要把票送給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 拜託你這種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.20,0:08:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.60,0:08:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是開車去接你妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.80,0:08:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.80,0:08:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好我們租了一輛車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.50,0:08:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.30,0:08:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正巧我上午有工作要去很遠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.00,0:08:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太幸運了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 不知道美菜她怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.70,0:08:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前她明明還很期待這場演唱會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.70,0:08:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然沒去我們約好的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.10,0:08:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你有沒有打個電話給她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.30,0:08:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是都沒有人接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.00,0:08:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話答錄機也沒開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望她不要做什麼傻事才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.50,0:08:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.30,0:09:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我妹妹最近有點不對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.30,0:09:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她都已經決定要結婚了但老是提不起精神來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.70,0:09:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候還會莫名其妙地哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.20,0:09:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為這樣我才會約她今天去聽演唱會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.00,0:09:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為的就是要讓她散散心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.30,0:09:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我從剛才就一直想問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.30,0:09:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你戴在頭上的那條頭巾莫非是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.50,0:09:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是洋子昨天發行的專輯大碟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.00,0:09:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只隨初回限定版附贈的頭巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是洋子的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.40,0:09:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒想到你連這種東西都搜集到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.30,0:09:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.10,0:09:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作為她的粉絲竟然沒去買嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.80,0:09:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外她還送給我們這個鑰匙環呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的CD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.00,0:09:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為都是她本人送的 所以就沒有贈品了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.70,0:09:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人送的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說你跟洋子認識了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.20,0:09:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是因為某個案子認識的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.10,0:09:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.70,0:10:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.10,0:10:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼地方不對嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.90,0:10:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我以前就聽過你的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.40,0:10:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你實在太有名了所以我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.20,0:10:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏哪裏 你過獎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨門獨戶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說你妹妹獨自一人住在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.60,0:10:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.90,0:10:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到上周為止都是我跟我妹妹兩個人住在這裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.60,0:10:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從下個月開始這裏就是我妹妹和她未婚夫的新居了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.30,0:10:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要搬出去住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.40,0:10:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的鞋子還在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.70,0:10:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她一定還在睡覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.40,0:10:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我去叫我妹妹起床了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.10,0:11:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.10,0:11:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到客廳裏隨便坐坐好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.30,0:11:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是時間…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.90,0:11:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.50,0:11:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離開場只有一個小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.00,0:11:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 事到如今你就別著急了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.00,0:11:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這些是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.60,0:11:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個房間都是偶像明星的海報啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.90,0:11:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有洋子小姐的 安西明日香的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.40,0:11:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TWO-MIX的 星野輝美的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連已經解散的雷克斯的都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.80,0:11:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你連這些都知道那才叫厲害呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.20,0:11:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來全代小姐真的是追星族啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.30,0:11:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她妹妹跟她住在一起可就彆扭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩個好像都喜歡這個的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.50,0:11:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.70,0:11:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是寫真集還是CD都是雙份的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且上面還有她們的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.30,0:12:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是全代小姐為什麼不把這些搬到新家去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.60,0:12:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定是因為數量太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法一次都帶走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.80,0:12:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.00,0:12:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些用來搬家的紙箱還剩這麼多...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.30,0:12:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜 美菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.70,0:12:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.70,0:12:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.50,0:12:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開門啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.30,0:12:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜 美菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.80,0:12:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.70,0:12:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(永別了)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是從裏面上鎖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.70,0:12:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這扇門根本沒有裝鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.10,0:12:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我看這扇門好像是從裏面用膠帶把門縫全部貼住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.40,0:12:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們一起來把門撞開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自…自殺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.40,0:13:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭 報警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.20,0:13:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快報警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.10,0:13:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.60,0:13:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹她還有救嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.90,0:13:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常遺憾 她已經斷氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.80,0:13:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.60,0:13:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室的窗子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.40,0:13:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有門口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都用膠帶給貼起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.10,0:13:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且地板上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.10,0:13:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有兩種蓋子打開了的浴室清潔劑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.00,0:13:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道真是自殺...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.40,0:13:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過死者手腕上的傷口很可疑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.60,0:13:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這絕對不是自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.60,0:14:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是他殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.90,0:14:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我搞不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.80,0:14:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是這樣的話兇手是怎樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.50,0:14:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎樣從浴室裏逃出去的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.10,0:14:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個空間明明都用膠帶給封死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.20,0:14:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎樣做到的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.20,0:14:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者是青島美菜 24歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.40,0:14:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死因是左手手腕的切傷所引起的動脈破裂而造成的失血過多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.90,0:14:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於發現死者的是她的姐姐全代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.80,0:14:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.70,0:14:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 就是又因為巧合而出現在這裏的我們這位…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.10,0:14:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是全代小姐拜託我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.60,0:14:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開車到這裏來接她妹妹的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.40,0:14:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現浴室這裏不太對勁才衝進來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.60,0:15:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所謂的不太對勁是指浴室的門窗上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.70,0:15:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都貼滿了膠布吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.00,0:15:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 從浴室內部把縫隙全部貼滿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.70,0:15:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使這裏成了一個完全的密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.70,0:15:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這是自殺絕對錯不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.90,0:15:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過按常理推斷一個會割腕自殺的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.90,0:15:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要把這裏完全給密封起來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.60,0:15:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是因為死者以為氯化物和酸性成分的 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.80,0:15:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室清潔劑混合了之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.80,0:15:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會產生有毒的氯氣的原因吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.30,0:15:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她把這裏密封起來就是為了不讓氣體外洩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.60,0:15:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是毛利老弟 這兩種都是氯化物成分的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.70,0:15:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.30,0:15:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真有氯氣產生就算把這裏封起來也是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.40,0:15:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.90,0:15:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位死去的美菜小姐可不像我們這麼專業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼會知道氯氣的威力有多大呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我覺得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我認為美菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.80,0:15:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在自殺前就已經有些精神錯亂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說真相是這樣子的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.50,0:16:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她計畫好自殺後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.30,0:16:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把這兩種浴室清潔劑準備好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.20,0:16:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她事先把浴室的縫隙全都封起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.70,0:16:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為她在氣體產生時才注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.90,0:16:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她買回來的根本不是她想要的浴室清潔劑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.30,0:16:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是在無計可施的情況下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.10,0:16:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就用浴室裏本來就有的剃刀割腕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.40,0:16:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手放進熱水裏好讓自己快點因為失血過多而死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官 你看看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.30,0:16:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是掉在客廳裏的收據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.00,0:16:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這上面的兩種浴室清潔劑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.10,0:16:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有膠帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.60,0:16:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是美菜小姐昨晚到便利商店買來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.20,0:16:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是她想自殺而匆忙去準備的有力證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.70,0:16:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.20,0:16:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.30,0:16:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到這家便利商店去確認一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.70,0:16:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.50,0:16:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠帶剩下的部分我們已經從浴缸裏找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說美菜小姐真是在匆忙之下完成這一切的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.70,0:17:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼沒有考慮到這些也就說得通了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.40,0:17:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這個大姐姐也太匆忙了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.20,0:17:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個大姐姐的手腕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.00,0:17:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的切痕真是太亂了喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.00,0:17:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.70,0:17:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說企圖自殺又猶豫不決的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.00,0:17:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劃下的傷痕跟致命的傷痕幾乎都是平行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.40,0:17:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會像這樣有這麼大的交叉才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.90,0:17:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼看來該不會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.70,0:17:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是巧合而已啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.90,0:17:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就表示美菜小姐在自殺時真的有點錯亂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.90,0:17:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果這樣的話她還會打掃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.30,0:17:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打掃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.80,0:17:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們自己看這些血嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.80,0:17:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在離水面高一點的地方有一條直直的線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.10,0:17:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就表示在血濺出來以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個大姐姐還用什麼東西把血擦掉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.10,0:17:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 一個要自殺的人怎麼會做這種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.50,0:18:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那血跡為什麼會那麼直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.50,0:18:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是在血濺出來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個地方剛好放了什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.80,0:18:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.80,0:18:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她割腕的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.50,0:18:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好有個人站在她旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.10,0:18:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.10,0:18:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官 這該不會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.50,0:18:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有他殺的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是因為膠帶呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.10,0:18:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是在浴缸裏發現了那卷膠帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.10,0:18:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.00,0:18:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說她原本是把那卷膠帶放在浴缸旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.60,0:18:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在割腕之後才不小心把膠帶碰掉的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.50,0:18:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以說得通了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.10,0:18:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太感謝你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.70,0:18:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧有了你 我們才能把這個謎題解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.80,0:18:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.20,0:18:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.00,0:18:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這膠帶上所留下的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.40,0:19:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有美菜小姐一個人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.80,0:19:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個膠帶的切口這裏 她兩手的食指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.90,0:19:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有拇指的指紋都清晰地附在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.30,0:19:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.30,0:19:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 這個"永別"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.30,0:19:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以看作美菜小姐的遺言了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.50,0:19:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來她真是自殺的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.40,0:19:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用問嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.30,0:19:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這間浴室根本就是密室嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.30,0:19:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差點忘掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.70,0:19:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊 毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.50,0:19:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.30,0:19:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候你對我說過的話應該沒有忘記吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.50,0:19:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋子小姐今晚演唱會的門票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.50,0:19:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你答應要讓給我一張的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託爸爸 都什麼時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.40,0:19:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.10,0:19:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在趕過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.60,0:19:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少還能看到演唱會的最後一首歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.20,0:19:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我現在去拿票吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.20,0:20:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我妹妹應該把門票放在客廳裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.70,0:20:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些紙箱上面都已經有折痕了 是不是已經用過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.20,0:20:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為之前要搬的東西太多了 所以我又拿回來用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.20,0:20:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.20,0:20:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那個時候你妹妹就幫你整理東西了對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.80,0:20:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那張桌子邊緣都黏黏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.80,0:20:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是膠帶黏在上面留下的痕跡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.40,0:20:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說有人先幫你把膠帶剪好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.40,0:20:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整齊地排在桌子邊緣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.30,0:20:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要打包起來就方便多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你在哪裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.10,0:20:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的那個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.10,0:21:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.60,0:21:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.10,0:21:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…弟弟 你姐姐在叫你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.40,0:21:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶 我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.90,0:21:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要把膠帶的痕跡去掉也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我剛才跟鑑識科的人說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.10,0:21:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們早就已經拍下這裏的照片了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.10,0:21:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你在這裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.80,0:21:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.80,0:21:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 大姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.50,0:21:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.20,0:21:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你真是的 跟你說過不要亂跑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.20,0:21:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對錯不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.70,0:21:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.50,0:21:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 殺死美菜小姐的兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.80,0:22:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是全代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.90,0:22:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我沒弄明白的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.20,0:22:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室被膠帶封成了密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.20,0:22:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她是怎麼出去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.50,0:22:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外還一個有地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.00,0:22:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我一直覺得不對勁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.60,0:22:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個奇怪的地方是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.70,0:23:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 那個是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.90,0:23:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個是…莫非…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.00,0:23:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 美菜小姐不是自殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.30,0:23:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是被人殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.10,0:24:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她的姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.50,0:24:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全代小姐就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.60,0:24:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.90,0:24:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室密室事件(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.70,0:24:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.60,0:24:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.10,0:24:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集是後篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.90,0:24:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手是身為未婚夫的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.90,0:24:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 不是說了是全代小姐嗎
